{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":492,"text":"The entire model of capitalism"},{"time":3924,"text":"and the economic model that you and I"},{"time":6103,"text":"did business in,"},{"time":7782,"text":"and, in fact, continue to do business in,"},{"time":9609,"text":"was built around what probably Milton Friedman"},{"time":13232,"text":"put more succinctly."},{"time":14950,"text":"And Adam Smith, of course, \nthe father of modern economics"},{"time":17530,"text":"actually said many, many years ago,"},{"time":19879,"text":"the invisible hand,"},{"time":21397,"text":"which is, \"If you continue to operate"},{"time":23053,"text":"in your own self-interest"},{"time":25166,"text":"you will do the best good for society.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":27922,"text":"Now, capitalism has done a lot of good things"},{"time":32653,"text":"and I've talked about a lot of good \nthings that have happened,"},{"time":35455,"text":"but equally, it has not been able to meet up"},{"time":38841,"text":"with some of the challenges that we've seen"},{"time":40777,"text":"in society."},{"time":42438,"text":"The model that at least I was brought up in"},{"time":44652,"text":"and a lot of us doing\nbusiness were brought up in"},{"time":46932,"text":"was one which talked about"},{"time":48641,"text":"what I call the three G's of growth:"},{"time":51069,"text":"growth that is consistent,\n"},{"time":52658,"text":"quarter on quarter;"},{"time":54184,"text":"growth that is competitive,"},{"time":55622,"text":"better than the other person;"},{"time":56952,"text":"and growth that is profitable,"},{"time":58514,"text":"so you continue to make"},{"time":60003,"text":"more and more shareholder value."},{"time":62922,"text":"And I'm afraid this is not going to be good enough"},{"time":65714,"text":"and we have to move from this 3G model"},{"time":68374,"text":"to a model of what I call"},{"time":70688,"text":"the fourth G:"},{"time":72234,"text":"the G of growth that is responsible."},{"time":76123,"text":"And it is this that has to become"},{"time":79560,"text":"a very important part"},{"time":81800,"text":"of creating value."},{"time":83675,"text":"Of not just creating economic value"},{"time":86400,"text":"but creating social value."},{"time":88854,"text":"And companies that will thrive are those"},{"time":91654,"text":"that will actually embrace the fourth G."},{"time":95019,"text":"And the model of 4G is quite simple:"},{"time":98044,"text":"Companies cannot afford \nto be just innocent bystanders"},{"time":101816,"text":"in what's happening around in society."},{"time":104151,"text":"They have to begin to play their role"},{"time":107718,"text":"in terms of serving the communities"},{"time":109878,"text":"which actually sustain them."},{"time":111976,"text":"And we have to move to a model"},{"time":113673,"text":"of an and/and model which is"},{"time":115766,"text":"how do we make money and do good?"},{"time":119248,"text":"How do we make sure"},{"time":121056,"text":"that we have a great business"},{"time":122636,"text":"but we also have a great environment around us?"},{"time":125508,"text":"And that model"},{"time":126828,"text":"is all about doing well and doing good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129797,"text":"But the question is easier said than done."},{"time":132118,"text":"But how do we actually get that done?"},{"time":134255,"text":"And I do believe"},{"time":135601,"text":"that the answer to that is going to be leadership."},{"time":138691,"text":"It is going to be to redefine"},{"time":140048,"text":"the new business models"},{"time":141918,"text":"which understand"},{"time":143264,"text":"that the only license to operate"},{"time":145269,"text":"is to combine these things."},{"time":147406,"text":"And for that you need businesses"},{"time":149338,"text":"that can actually define their role"},{"time":152097,"text":"in society"},{"time":154182,"text":"in terms of a much larger purpose"},{"time":155826,"text":"than the products and brands that they sell."},{"time":158657,"text":"And companies that actually define a true north,"},{"time":161890,"text":"things that are nonnegotiable"},{"time":163636,"text":"whether times are good, bad, ugly --"},{"time":166196,"text":"doesn't matter."},{"time":167463,"text":"There are things that you stand for."},{"time":169629,"text":"Values and purpose are going to be the two"},{"time":174121,"text":"drivers of software"},{"time":176256,"text":"that are going to create"},{"time":177968,"text":"the companies of tomorrow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":180034,"text":"And I'm going to now shift"},{"time":181440,"text":"to talking a little bit about my own experiences."},{"time":185458,"text":"I joined Unilever in 1976"},{"time":188338,"text":"as a management trainee in India."},{"time":191471,"text":"And on my first day of work"},{"time":193806,"text":"I walked in and my boss tells me,"},{"time":196140,"text":"\"Do you know why you're here?\""},{"time":198247,"text":"I said, \"I'm here to sell a lot of soap.\""},{"time":201544,"text":"And he said, \n\"No, you're here to change lives.\""},{"time":204630,"text":"You're here to change lives."},{"time":206922,"text":"You know, I thought it was rather facetious."},{"time":208552,"text":"We are a company that sells soap and soup."},{"time":211367,"text":"What are we doing about changing lives?"},{"time":214239,"text":"And it's then I realized"},{"time":218254,"text":"that simple acts"},{"time":220577,"text":"like selling a bar of soap"},{"time":223009,"text":"can save more lives"},{"time":224498,"text":"than pharmaceutical companies."},{"time":225975,"text":"I don't know how many of you know"},{"time":227597,"text":"that five million children don't reach the age of five"},{"time":230932,"text":"because of simple infections that can be prevented"},{"time":233808,"text":"by an act of washing their hands with soap."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236748,"text":"We run the largest"},{"time":238200,"text":"hand-washing program"},{"time":239429,"text":"in the world."},{"time":240334,"text":"We are running a program on hygiene and health"},{"time":242495,"text":"that now touches half a billion people."},{"time":244997,"text":"It's not about selling soap,"},{"time":246597,"text":"there is a larger purpose out there."},{"time":248558,"text":"And brands indeed can be"},{"time":250616,"text":"at the forefront of social change."},{"time":252623,"text":"And the reason for that is,"},{"time":254280,"text":"when two billion people use your brands"},{"time":256890,"text":"that's the amplifier."},{"time":258542,"text":"Small actions can make a big difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261743,"text":"Take another example,"},{"time":263281,"text":"I was walking around in \none of our villages in India."},{"time":266551,"text":"Now those of you who have done this"},{"time":268194,"text":"will realize that this is no walk in the park."},{"time":273368,"text":"And we had this lady"},{"time":275943,"text":"who was one of our small distributors --"},{"time":280083,"text":"beautiful, very, very modest, her home --"},{"time":283695,"text":"and she was out there,"},{"time":286103,"text":"dressed nicely,"},{"time":287655,"text":"her husband in the back, her mother-in-law behind"},{"time":289815,"text":"and her sister-in-law behind her."},{"time":292041,"text":"The social order was changing"},{"time":294113,"text":"because this lady"},{"time":295863,"text":"is part of our Project Shakti"},{"time":297999,"text":"that is actually teaching women"},{"time":300283,"text":"how to do small business"},{"time":302154,"text":"and how to carry the message"},{"time":303333,"text":"of nutrition and hygiene."},{"time":305976,"text":"We have 60,000 such women"},{"time":308183,"text":"now in India."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310035,"text":"It's not about selling soap,"},{"time":312488,"text":"it's about making sure"},{"time":313941,"text":"that in the process of doing so"},{"time":315981,"text":"you can change people's lives."},{"time":318174,"text":"Small actions, big difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321371,"text":"Our R&amp;D folks"},{"time":323090,"text":"are not only working to give us \nsome fantastic detergents,"},{"time":326719,"text":"but they're working to make sure we use less water."},{"time":329488,"text":"A product that we've just launched recently,"},{"time":331652,"text":"One Rinse product that allows you to save water"},{"time":335180,"text":"every time you wash your clothes."},{"time":337356,"text":"And if we can convert all our users to using this,"},{"time":340381,"text":"that's 500 billion liters of water."},{"time":342614,"text":"By the way, that's equivalent to one month of water"},{"time":344908,"text":"for a whole huge continent."},{"time":348092,"text":"So just think about it."},{"time":349768,"text":"There are small actions that \ncan make a big difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353335,"text":"And I can go on and on."},{"time":354953,"text":"Our food chain, our brilliant products --"},{"time":357050,"text":"and I'm sorry I'm giving you \na word from the sponsors --"},{"time":359419,"text":"Knorr, Hellman's and all those wonderful products."},{"time":363121,"text":"We are committed to making sure that"},{"time":365181,"text":"all our agricultural raw materials"},{"time":367138,"text":"are sourced from sustainable sources,"},{"time":369944,"text":"100-percent sustainable sources."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372044,"text":"We were the first"},{"time":373592,"text":"to say we are going to buy all of our palm oil"},{"time":375801,"text":"from sustainable sources."},{"time":377763,"text":"I don't know how many of you know that palm oil,"},{"time":381683,"text":"and not buying it from sustainable sources,"},{"time":384096,"text":"can create deforestation that is responsible"},{"time":386701,"text":"for 20 percent of the greenhouse gasses in the world."},{"time":389243,"text":"We were the first to embrace that,"},{"time":391759,"text":"and it's all because we market soap and soup."},{"time":396157,"text":"And the point I'm making here"},{"time":398355,"text":"is that companies like yours, companies like mine"},{"time":401878,"text":"have to define a purpose"},{"time":404001,"text":"which embraces responsibility"},{"time":406282,"text":"and understands that we have to play our part"},{"time":408982,"text":"in the communities in which we operate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411819,"text":"We introduced something called"},{"time":413719,"text":"The Unilever Sustainable Living Plan, which said,"},{"time":416463,"text":"\"Our purpose is to make \nsustainable living commonplace,"},{"time":419349,"text":"and we are gong to change the lives"},{"time":421176,"text":"of one billion people over 2020.\""},{"time":423901,"text":"Now the question here is,"},{"time":425701,"text":"where do we go from here?"},{"time":427225,"text":"And the answer to that is very simple:"},{"time":429145,"text":"We're not going to change the world alone."},{"time":431278,"text":"There are plenty of you and plenty of us"},{"time":433868,"text":"who understand this."},{"time":435338,"text":"The question is,"},{"time":436503,"text":"we need partnerships, we need coalitions"},{"time":439134,"text":"and importantly, we need that leadership"},{"time":441590,"text":"that will allow us to take this from here"},{"time":444550,"text":"and to be the change"},{"time":445839,"text":"that we want to see around us."},{"time":447375,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":448695,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}